{"tid":1542913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：不認同另設獨立調查委員會調查警方工作","createTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:30:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5a82dce16abaa5801fb54eb228a1b442584187d1","tid":1542913,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥說，政府對於五大訴求的回應，昨日她已清楚講明，除了正式撤回修訂，其餘的四大訴求，例如是釋放所有被捕及被控人士，是違反法治精神，根本不能夠做。<br />\n<br />\n她重申，事件必須交由現時的法定獨立機制去處理，不認同另設獨立調查委員會去調查警方工作。至於為何沒有委任泛民背景人士加入監警會，林鄭月娥指在現時社會對立、立場先行的情況下，監警會成員應該更中立，認為無政治背景的人士較為適合，但不代表日後政府不會以更包容的取態進行委任。"},{"pid":"7adbbc8cfb301b39978c7483d25c205f251ec4fe","tid":1542913,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1165051&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1165051%26csid%3D261_341&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=960d7252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1165051&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"982854b7a1dea0b12502df6076f3c0ac494dd053","tid":1542913,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /